Tandem Mixed License Notice

This repository uses a mixed licensing model. Different directories and
packages are governed by different license terms.

Permissive open-source components are licensed under MIT, Apache-2.0, or
MIT OR Apache-2.0 as declared in their package manifests.

Source-available components are licensed under the Business Source License
1.1 (SPDX: BUSL-1.1) as declared in their package manifests and local
LICENSE files.

Canonical licensing map:

  docs/LICENSING.md

License texts:

  LICENSE-MIT
  LICENSE-APACHE
  crates/tandem-plan-compiler/LICENSE
  crates/tandem-governance-engine/LICENSE

If a package manifest and this summary ever disagree, the package manifest
and the package-local LICENSE file control for that package.
